        {
            "id": 6122736,
            "title": "台股創史高後 外資連4賣超千億元 反手敲進泛鴻海家族",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (22) 日 2 萬 4 千點曇花一現，終場下跌 197.66 點收最低 23764.47 點，外資再賣近 164 億元，自台股周一 (18 日) 創下 245154 點歷史新高後，外資連 4 天賣超共逾千億元。個股方面，外資今日賣超面板雙虎共逾 2.2 萬張，反手買超鴻海，以及轉投資的廣宇、合作夥伴東元等。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6122736/l/fddc01ecd76724acd54f91d7d8a024c3.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">台股創史高後 外資連4賣超千億元 反手敲進泛鴻海家族。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資賣超友達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2409-TW</a>)1.7 萬張、群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)5389 張，以及聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)1.06 萬張、凌陽 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2401:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2401\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2401-TW</a>)9983 張、宏達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2498:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2498\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2498-TW</a>)7714 張、華晶科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3059:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3059\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3059-TW</a>)6018 張等電子股。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另外，外資也賣超傳產指標台泥 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1101:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1101\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1101-TW</a>)1.46 萬張、台化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1326:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1326\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1326-TW</a>)1.12 萬張、陽明 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2609:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2609-TW</a>)8083 張等，金融股有中信金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2891:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2891\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2891-TW</a>)1.21 萬張、合庫金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5880:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5880\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5880-TW</a>)7370 張、國泰金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2882:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2882\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2882-TW</a>)5932 張、ETF 則以元大台灣 50(0050)1.46 萬張較大量。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外資買超廣宇 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2328:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2328\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2328-TW</a>)2.12 萬張最多，其次為東元 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1504:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1504\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1504-TW</a>)1.35 萬張、台玻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1802:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1802\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1802-TW</a>)9274 張、鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)6693 張、兆豐金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2886:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2886\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2886-TW</a>)6660 張、漢翔 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2634:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2634\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2634-TW</a>)5419 張、毅嘉 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2402:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2402\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2402-TW</a>)4963 張、京元電子 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2449:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2449\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2449-TW</a>)4354 張、台船 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2208:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2208\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2208-TW</a>)4197 張、永豐金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2890:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2890\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2890-TW</a>)4026 張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
